∣</mi><mi>s</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>m</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>u</mi><mo separator=\"true\">,</mo><mi>v</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">∣</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">|sim(u,v)|</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">∣</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">s</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">im</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">u</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.03588em;\">v</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span><span class=\"mord\">∣</span></span></span></span> 表示相似度的绝对值（用于归一化）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"📏-usercf的核心算法\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#📏-usercf的核心算法\"><span>📏 UserCF的核心算法</span></a></h2>\n<div class=\"hint-container tip\">\n<p class=\"hint-container-title\">参考协同过滤总览</p>\n<p>详细的相似度计算方法请参考 <RouteLink to=\"/zh/3.%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%89%E7%AB%A0%EF%BC%9A%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95--%E6%AF%94%E4%BD%A0%E6%9B%B4%E6%87%82%E4%BD%A0%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%B4%E5%BF%83%E5%B0%8F%E6%A3%89%E8%A2%84/1.%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E7%AE%97%E6%B3%95%E7%9A%84%E9%97%A8%E6%B4%BE/2.collaborative_filtering.html#%E7%9B%B8%E4%BC%BC%E5%BA%A6%E5%BA%A6%E9%87%8F%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E8%AF%A6%E7%BB%86%E5%AF%B9%E6%AF%94\">协同过滤总览</RouteLink> 中的完整对比分析。</p>\n</div>\n<p>UserCF的关键在于准确计算用户间相似度，推荐选择：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>显式评分场景</strong>：优先使用皮尔逊相关系数</li>\n<li><strong>隐式反馈场景</strong>：优先使用余弦相似度</li>\n<li><strong>评分分布不均</strong>：考虑调整余弦相似度</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"💻-usercf算法实现\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#💻-usercf算法实现\"><span>💻 UserCF算法实现</span></a></h2>\n<details class=\"hint-container details\"><summary>UserCF核心算法框架</summary>\n<div class=\"language-python line-numbers-mode\" data-highlighter=\"shi